      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i see the null pointer but i'm stuck on why it's intermittent. like, some codes work fine and others dont. the DB lookup seems to work most of the time. could it be a race condition or maybe a weird edge case with how we're parsing the request body? what else should i check?",
